<section class="about-sec">
    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Wish List</h2>
        <p>
            Find a book that would be perfect for a friend? How about your parents or siblings or children?
            Want a book but don't want to buy it yet? The Bookstore now features our very own wishlist!
            Simply register an account and start adding books to your wishlist!
        </p>
        <div class="btn-sec">
            <a class="btn black" asp-area="" asp-controller="CartItems" asp-action="WishListIndex">Wish List</a>
            <a class="btn black" asp-area="" asp-controller="Search" asp-action="Index">Shop Books</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features-sec">
    <div class="container">
        <ul>
            <li>
                <span class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </span>
                <h3>Newest Titles out there</h3>
                <h5>We're stocked up</h5>
                <h6>You can be sure that we have the latest books on shelf and are constantly adding new titles daily </h6>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="icon return">
                    <i class="fa fa-reply-all" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </span>
                <h3>2 Week Shipping</h3>
                <h5>Fast Shipping Guaranteed</h5>
                <h6>We guarantee your book will reach your hands to be read in 2 weeks or less, or your money back guaranteed </h6>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="icon chat">
                    <i class="fa fa-comments" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </span>
                <h3>Active Support</h3>
                <h5>Our team is active</h5>
                <h6>Need helping picking a book? confused on what genres are out there? we're available for all questions </h6>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-sec">
    <div class="about-img">
        <figure style="background: url(/images/privacy.jpg)no-repeat;background-size: 100%"></figure>

    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Our Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We know your information is important to you. That is why we take the utmost pride in the
            security of your information and the protection of your shopping information.
            If you wish to learn more about our privacy policy, check out our privacy policy page.
        </p>
        <div class="btn-sec">
            <a class="btn black" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>